    "The prompt-llm-description prompt is generated by GPT-4o, expanding each personality trait into a short behavioral description: \"You are a person with level trait.",
    "Write a 50-word paragraph describing character traits or behaviors that reflect your trait.\"",
    "SFT-Prompt-Demo and DPO-Prompt-Demo represent demonstration-based prompting applied to SFT and DPO-trained models, respectively.",
    "Results for GPT-4o-mini and GPT-4o are presented in separate sections of the table.",
    "Scores range from 1 to 5, where a score closer to 5 indicates stronger agreement with the trait, while a score closer to 1 reflects weaker or opposing agreement."
